的专题节目<i>《午夜之后》</i>中露面时，进一步讨论了参加网络钓鱼节目的问题。 “这个周末我在 Sphere 看到了 Phish。没见过菲什。不知道网络钓鱼曲调。他们让我大吃一惊，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3552536" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552536" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552536" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio.jpg" alt="Phish 的 Trey Anastasio（摄影：Keith Griner/Getty Images for ABA）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2023-Phish-Trey-Anastasio-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3552536" class="wp-caption-text"> Phish 的 Trey Anastasio（摄影：Keith Griner/Getty Images for ABA）</figcaption></figure><p> “这就像连续四天被边缘化一样。然后就在第四天结束时令人心碎的高潮之前，一位天使从天而降，加百列，他向你的手臂注射了该死的海洛因，他说，“现在祝你好运！”然后他离开了。然后你就会达到 15 分钟的高潮，同时你的眼球会从头上掉下来。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drew-carey-said-hed-stick-his-dick-in-a-blender-for-phish-so-they-sent-him-a-blender-3751438"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> Phish 将于 7 月 12 日发行他们的第 16 张录音室专辑《Evolve》，主打歌已于本月早些时候作为主打单曲发行。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drew-carey-says-phish-at-the-sphere-makes-u2-look-like-a-bar-band-3753046">德鲁·凯里 (Drew Carey) 称 Sphere 的 Phish 使 U2“看起来像一支酒吧乐队”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
