/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/co-op-live-building@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/co-op-live-building@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/co-op-live-building@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/co-op-live-building@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/co-op-live-building@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Co-Op Group 就曼彻斯特 Co-Op Live Arena 的开放问题及其在场馆中所扮演的角色发表了一份声明。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-own-fyre-festival-disappointed-fans-speak-out-on-co-op-live-cancellations-3752712">“曼彻斯特自己的 Fyre 音乐节”——失望的球迷对 Co-Op Live 取消表示不满</a></strong></li></ul><p>Co-Op Live Arena 最近面临多次音乐会取消以及开放延迟的问题。该场馆原定<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-new-co-op-live-arena-regretfully-postpone-opening-shows-from-peter-kay-3749399">于 4 月 23 日至 24 日由喜剧演员彼得·凯 (Peter Kay) 主持开幕</a>，但演出被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-new-co-op-live-arena-regretfully-postpone-opening-shows-from-peter-kay-3749399">推迟到 4 月底</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rick-astley-opens-uks-new-biggest-indoor-arena-in-manchester-after-some-test-gig-tickets-were-axed-for-fans-3749324">在 4 月 22 日与里克·阿斯特利 (Rick Astley) 进行测试活动</a>后，现在又推迟到本月晚些时候。然后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-co-op-live-arena-sees-further-problems-and-delays-as-the-black-keys-and-peter-kay-forced-to-postpone-shows-3751134">原定于 4 月 27 日在该场馆观看 The Black Keys 的表演</a>；他们的演出移至5月15日。</p><p> 5月1日，由于“场地相关技术问题”，该场馆<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-co-op-live-arena-pulls-a-boogie-wit-da-hoodie-show-last-minute-due-to-venue-related-technical-issue-3752508">在开业仅10分钟后就被迫取消了A Boogie Wit Da Hoodie的演出，</a>再次未能开业。其后<a href="https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/co-op-lives-first-show-29096609" target="_blank" rel="noopener">经场馆发言人证实，这是掉落在场馆内的空调的一部分</a>；没有人受伤。自从发现故障装置以来，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keane">基恩 (Keane</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">Take That</a>在 Co-Op Live 上的演出都已被证实被取消。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752996" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752996" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752996" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024.jpg" alt="曼彻斯特 Co-op Live 的照片（摄影：Jeff Spicer/Getty Images for Co-op Live）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Co-Op-Live-Venue-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752996" class="wp-caption-text">曼彻斯特 Co-op Live 的照片（摄影：Jeff Spicer/Getty Images for Co-op Live）</figcaption></figure><p>现在，Co-Op 集团发言人澄清了冠名赞助商在场馆中的角色，并解决了开幕问题：“作为 Co-Op Live 的冠名权赞助商，我们对这些进一步的日程变化感到失望。我们完全理解并理解延误对持票人和我们的合作社会员造成的影响和不安。”</p><p>该发言人继续说道：“Co-Op 是赞助商，并不拥有或经营该场馆，我们已向负责该建筑的 Oak View Group 明确表示，必须优先考虑对持票人的影响。我们很高兴他们很快就会制定计划来实现这一目标。”</p><p> Co-Op 集团表示：“我们还了解到，昨天事件发生后必要的安全检查正在完成并进行独立验证，以便 Co-Op 会员和其他持票人可以放心，该场馆拥有最高级别的安保和安全措施。”发言人总结道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752649" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752649" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752649" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads